The paper also involves computer vision applications, which suggests cs.CV (Computer Vision) as the second likely sub-category. The paper also employs geodesic distance and KL-divergence, which are concepts from information theory, suggesting cs.IT (Information Theory) as the third likely sub-category. The paper also involves optimization techniques, which suggests cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as the fourth likely sub-category. Finally, the paper involves statistical analysis, which suggests cs.ST (Statistics) as the fifth likely sub-category.
